E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Here we go again. Blah blah blah... put on a new record, DJ.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~这集看过了。废话废话废话...老板换碟。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~But I think you spoke about some shit so you took a walk and I, who didn't talk, I took a fall, and I don't care.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~但我还是觉得你说了些什么，所以才逍遥法外。而我啥都没说，就坐牢了，但我不在乎。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~All I was saying is that it's cool to hang out and you've got to both act like a pair of fucking women.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~我只是想说能一起出来玩真好，结果你们俩都跟泼妇似的。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Oye, I only saw her a minute, man. She came down to Maisonette.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~喂，我们只聊了一会儿，哥们。她来9号豪宅了。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Cool. Living and dying for dope... with no hope of nothing better. Seems kind of pathetic to me.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~行吧。到死都在贩毒...看不见别的盼头。我觉得有点可悲。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Oye, I help when I can. You know that.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~喂，有空了我就来帮忙。你知道的。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~You ain't losing me, bro. I took a fucking fall for you, you dumb, ingrate prick, and we still friends,
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~你不会失去我的，兄弟。我都替你坐过牢了，你个忘恩负义的傻逼。咱们还是朋友，

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~I mean why you fucking stupid, bro. Is it 'cause your momma was smoking crack while she had you,
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~我问的是你为什么是白痴，兄弟。是你妈怀你的时候吸可卡因把你吸傻了，

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~So you'll understand that maybe sometimes I like things to be a little mellower.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~那你总该明白，我也会希望各方面都能稳重一点吧。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~That he all growed up while we still the same as we were as kids. He too good for us.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~逼他说「我已经长大了，但你们还是当年的小屁孩。你们配不上我。」

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Oh shut up. Both of you. You're both as bad as each other.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~噢，你俩都闭嘴吧。别五十步笑百步了。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Why did I spend a chunk of my life inside, and you didn't?
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~怎么我花了大把时间坐牢，你却没有？

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Careful, man. I'm sick. Who knows what I could do?
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~哈哈，小心点，哥们。我可是变态啊。天知道我会干出啥事？

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Like my dad for starters and my mom for second. If the Island life don't grab you, bro,
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~我爸是第一个，然后就是我妈。就算你没被岛上的生活留住，兄弟，

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Fuck you, little asshole. I ain't a moron.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~操你妈，小逼崽子，我不是傻子。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Maybe we is going different directions right now, but that don't mean I think I'm better than you.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~也许我们现在是走在不同的路上，哥们，但这不代表我觉得自己比你们高贵啊。
~z~我认真的。咋的了？说实话，兄弟。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Me neither, but I'd rather die trying to get out of this world, than stuck in it, you know what I mean?
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~我也不想啊，兄弟。但我宁可死在脱离街头的路上，也不想待在这里。你懂我意思吧？

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~So, like, when you coming on board full time. When we talking the operation to the next level?
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~那个，你什么时候能加入我们？我们什么时候采取进一步的行动？

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~You guys. We supposed to be having a good time. What's got into you?
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~你俩别吵了。我们是出来休闲放松的，都犯啥病呢？

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Well, you certainly seem to like angry asshole, so I see what you mean.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~确实，你好像是挺喜欢暴脾气的人，我能懂你的意思。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Well you should do, 'cause it's fucking true.
~z~Listen, I know you didn't rat me out. If I thought you had, I would have killed you.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~听着，我知道你没出卖我。我要真那么想，你早就死了。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Ended up cornering Jimmy Boston and crying her eyes out. Telling him she hated her life.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~最后把Jimmy Boston逼到墙角，自己哭得稀里哗啦的。一直在说日子有多难过。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~I been meaning to ask you, L. How your tight-ass hermano feel about your current situation.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~我一直都想问你，L，你那铁公鸡兄弟对你的现状有啥看法。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Part of making Luis tell us that he ain't like us no more.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~逼着Luis告诉我们「我和你们没感情了。」

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~I mean - what the fuck is wrong with you? You have that little self awareness.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~我是说，你他妈有病吧？一点自知之明都没有。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Must really get that dorky motherfucker's back up.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~那傻逼玩意肯定会气得跳脚。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~At least I got a momma, A. Least mine didn't run out on me.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~至少我还有妈，A。我妈可没抛下我走人，A。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Fuck you, Armando. Why you so angry?
~z~Listen that faggot cage fighting bullshit may work with a bunch of Russian models,
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~听着，你的基佬笼中斗冠军也许能骗到不少毛妹模特，

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~You being weird, A. Rique can go wherever the fuck he likes.
~z~What you mean? Why is he, like, the most dependable motherfucker to have around in the fight?
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~这样是哪样？是说为什么他会成为你能找到的最可靠的打手吗？

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~I just told you - we making moves.
~z~And what's your excuse, A? For being a moron, I mean...
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~那你的原因呢，A？我是说你傻逼的原因...

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Man, we gonna have some fucking fun, right?
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~哥们，咱们得他妈找点乐子，对吧？

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~What, now you're going to get all in my face and act like the hard man, huh son?
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~怎么，现在你要跟我耍横装硬汉了，小子？

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Yes, I got that bit, fool. What I meant was how you and Henrique B planning on doing next?
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~对，我听见了，傻逼。我要问的是你和Henrique接下来有什么打算？

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Yeah, sorry H. And he's right. It is good to hang out.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~是的，对不起，H。他说得对，能一起出来真好。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Yo. You remember when he caught us trying to get into Mr. Ellis's house?
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~哟，你还记得他发现咱们想溜进Ellis老师家那次吗？

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Yeah, bro. I don't think my brother like my situation.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~是啊，兄弟。我觉的我哥不喜欢我的现状。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Oye, you got some real abandonment issues you got to deal with, Armando. Damn.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~我说，你的不安全感也太严重了吧，该治治了，Armando。妈的。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Mingling with all these celebrities. We give you shit, but it's kind of impressive.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~你整天都在和名人厮混啊。我们是没啥感觉，但别人不这么想啊。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Shit, A. You can come too, if you like.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~妈的，A。你要是乐意的话，可以一起去。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Jimmy Boston? He a good actor, bro.
~z~We been making serious moves, dude. Serious shit.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~我们一步一个脚印，哥们。在往前走。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~I'd ask him to do the accounts for the club, but I'd be worried the motherfucker would report us to the IRS.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~我有想过找他给夜店管账，但我担心这傻逼会向国税局举报我们。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Not sure. Sometimes I think okay, and sometimes I think fucking awful, bro.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~说不清，哥们。有时感觉还行，有时又感觉不行，兄弟。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~He's so fucking gay, he probably pissed he didn't spend longer inside.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~他这么个基佬，估计还嫌弃自己没在牢里多待几年。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Well, whatever, it certainly impacted you. Now you love hanging with fags.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~那不重要，但监狱一定让你变了。现在你喜欢跟着基佬一起混。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~But if you get all street philosopher on me, I am going to beat your bitch ass black and fucking blue.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~要是你敢跟我耍街头的那点小聪明，我他妈就把你揍得青一块紫一块。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~you gonna get shot by a third world cop, or you'll drown your dumb ass. You ain't fucking leaving me.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~你要么吃第三世界警察的枪子，要么就是掉水里淹死。你他妈别想走。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Don't look down on her for that shit. Not everyone as acclimatized to the fancy-ass celebrity scene as you are, bro.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~别因为这事看不起她。不是所有人都跟你一样能在名人面前如鱼得水的。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~The kind you're too cool to tell us about, huh?
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~就是你那些酷到不能告诉我们的事？

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~It ain't your fault. Whole neighborhood knows you got dropped out of a window when you was baby...
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~你傻不怪你。这里人都知道你小时候从窗户掉下去过...

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Jesus. I thought Henrique was the moron. I mean, gimme a break, L.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~天哪。亏我把Henrique当傻逼。别吧，放过我吧，L。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~He did always tell us we was never gonna be shit, didn't he?
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~他确实一直说我们会一事无成，不是吗？

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~I guess I'm just worried about losing my friends...
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~我想我只是担心失去自己的朋友...

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Sorry... know you don't do anything you don't enjoy.... I meant sucking them off.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~抱歉...我知道你只做自己喜欢的工作...我是指给别人口。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~but shit don't mean nothing up here.
~z~I know that, but you'd think she'd want to talk to family, not some guy from the movies.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~我知道，哥们。但她其实是想找家人说话，不是哪个电影明星。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Well that'swhat I'm aiming for, a mellow vibe.
~z~Who you calling a fool, you poseur. You always was. A pretty boy, but not a street guy.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~你说谁傻逼呢，伪君子？你一直都没变，是块小鲜肉，不是道上混的。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Me neither, bro. It's hard to get angry when there's such a glaring fault in your logic.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~我也不是，兄弟。你的逻辑里有明显错误，我很难生气。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~So you want to die on the streets, man? Cause that's how this will end for all of us, way we been living.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~那你是想横尸街头吗，哥们？咱们这种活法，到头来都是这样。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Any normal human being woulda helped our asses, not threatened to report us.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~是个正常人都会帮我们一把，而不是威胁说要去告状。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Rique, bro, why you think you like you are?
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~Rique，兄弟，你觉得为什么你会是现在这样？

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~I mean, we talking like rainforest depleting tree habit to pop me out.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~就是说，你那逻辑堪比因为雨林衰退，我才生成这样。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~You know, usual kind of chaotic shit.
~z~She have to smoke up inhuman amounts of weed to make a kid this stupid.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~她就算抽大麻抽到上天，都不至于把我生得这么笨。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~How about this, L? Me and Rique gonna stop trying to make you change, if pay us the same respect.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~那这样行不行，L？只要你也尊重我们，我和Rique就不再逼你回心转意了。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~ We was trying to rob a teacher, after all.
~z~It's bullshit. For real. This guy is just pent up cause Tony won't blow him no more.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~都是屁话，假的。就因为Tony不给他口，他开始自闭了。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~You ain't going, man. I told you that.
~z~Just don't drag H down with you, street genius, that's all.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~那你别把H也拖下水，街头天才。就这样。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~The movies is good, bro. I shout at the screen the whole time.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~他的电影很棒，兄弟。我一直对着屏幕大叫呢。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Yo, shit, bro. I'm sorry. I didn't mean nothing.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~哟，妈的，兄弟。对不起。我不是故意的。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Gentlemen... man, you spent too long wiping rich guy's asses.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~绅士？哥们，你给阔佬擦屁股擦多了吧。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Well I know all about that. I spend all day hanging with H.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~这个我熟。我每天都跟H一起出来。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~I might go back to the DR for a time. My pia say she wants some company.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~我应该回多米尼加待段时间了。我姑姑说她需要陪伴。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Maybe some people do. But, yeah, whatever, bro.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~也有人会变吧。不过确实，随便吧，兄弟。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Tell your hermana to hit we up when she next in town.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~哪天你妹妹来城里了记得让她联系我们。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~And it don't mean I can't help you guys go legit neither.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~也不代表我不愿意帮你们上岸改行。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Listen, I know you didn't get me in worse shit, but I do know you got someone in worse shit. And I don't give a fuck.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~听着，我知道你当年没害得我更糟，但我知道你害了别人。但我不在乎。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~You a kid who once broke his teacher's arm because the teaher picked on his sister.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~当年你可是因为妹妹被老师欺负，就打断了老师的胳膊啊。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~You might have forgotten, but I'm his boss, yo. We got a fuckin' business to run.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~你也许是忘了，但我可是他老板，哟。我们还他妈要做生意呢。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Good to be hanging with you again, L.
~z~Just bullshit to do with hanging out with idiots.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~就是些屁事，比如陪白痴出去。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Which is why I'm thinking of fucking killing you.
~z~And I ain't never not respected that, bro. I always treated you like the freak you are.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~我也没有不尊重过你的为人，兄弟。我只是给了怪人应有的待遇，哈哈。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~I told you not to do this, A. I told you I didn't wanna be no part of it.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~我都说了别这样了，A。我都说了我不想掺和进来。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~You got a point. I guess it was crack then.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~哈哈，很有道理。那就是可卡因的缘故了。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~I'm a street guy. Do I look like I got a 401K?
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~我可是街头混混。我像是有退休金的人吗？

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~It's the company I keep. Two giant, over muscled pea brains.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~近墨者黑。怪这俩四肢发达，头脑简单的家伙。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~You'd get a medal for that - services to humanity.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~那不得给你送面锦旗——为民除害。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Dope is a way to help yourself, not a life, least that's how I see it, but whatever you fools want.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~贩毒只是为了吃饭，不是生活方式。至少我是这么想的，你们俩傻逼爱咋咋。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~It's just for a few months. You get someone to fill in.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~就去几个月。你找个人来替吧。
~z~那他妈是老师啊。变态吧你，兄弟。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~We is who we is. End of story.
~z~Well, I went down and you didn't. So what was it, huh? Did you squeal?
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~当年我进去了，你没有。那算什么，啊？你丫告密了？

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Anyway, she was maybe a couple of months back on a conference.
~z~Jesus - that's funny coming from you. We hear what you've been getting up to. We know what you like.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~天哪，这话轮不到你说。我们知道你平常干什么，知道你是什么人。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~He's like that 'cause you the least dependable guy, A. And you always getting into us fuckin' fights.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~他变成这样，都是因为你太靠不住，A。而且你还整天给我们找架打。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~All the way. The three of us together.
~z~Thank you. No one ever called me a genius before.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~谢谢，还没有人说过我是天才呢。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~I guess I ain't so riddled with insecurity as you. I'm happy with who I am.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~大概我没你那么缺乏安全感。我对自己很满意。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~No fucking way. People go to the Island, they don't come back.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~门都没有。上了岛的人是不会回来的。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~You know that ain't how I think, H.
~z~You didn't take no fall for me.
~z~Yeah, only I hope with better results. Maybe this time, I can avoid a bid in a correctional facility.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~是啊，希望这次有更好的结果吧。说不定这次我不会被抓去坐牢。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Pair of fucking bitches. Always complaining and shit.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~跟俩泼妇一样，每天都在吵架。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Let's try to keep things cool, okay?
~z~I ain't talking "when you can". I'm talking ditch this other shit and we gonna make something go.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~我不是问你「哪天有空」。我的意思是让你抛下别的，我们一起干些大事。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~Way I see it, is you're lucky to be as bright as you are. You a genius, given half your brain probably got smashed.
E2FCAUD.translated: ~z~依我看，你能有现在这智商已经够走运了。你是个天才，考虑到你的脑子可能摔坏了一半的话。

E2FCAUD.original: ~z~even though we seem to hate each other.
~z~or was it just that weed smoke shit?
